104451754.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fgaza-border-crossing-set-to-reopen-as-israeli-troops-prepare-ground-assault%2Famp_articleshow%2F104451754.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arab%20States%20%26quot%3BDetermined%26quot%3B%20To%20Not%20Let%20Israel-Hamas%20War%20Spread%3A%20Antony%20Blinken%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20will%20return%20to%20Israel%20on%20Monday%20to%20talk%20%26quot%3Babout%20the%20way%20forward%26quot%3B%20after%20several%20days%20of%20shuttle%20diplomacy%20between%20Arab%20states%2C%20which%20he%20said%20shared%20the%20US%20determination%20to%20ensure%20Israel's%20conflict%20with%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%20does%20not%20spillover%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20US%20diplomat%20arrived%20in%20Israel%20on%20Thursday%20-%20as%20it%20prepares%20a%20ground%20offensive%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20retaliation%20for%20a%20deadly%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20civilians%20-%20and%20has%20also%20been%20to%20Qatar%2C%20Jordan%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20has%20raised%20international%20concern%20that%20it%20could%20spark%20a%20wider%20regional%20war%20as%20Iranian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Hossein%20Amirabdollahian%20warned%20on%20Sunday%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20hands%20of%20all%20parties%20in%20the%20region%20are%20on%20the%20trigger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20determination%20in%20every%20country%20I%20went%20to%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20this%20conflict%20doesn't%20spread%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20told%20reporters%20as%20he%20prepared%20to%20leave%20Cairo.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20using%20their%20own%20influence%2C%20their%20own%20relationships%2C%20to%20try%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20this%20doesn't%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBinken%20met%20with%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20in%20Riyadh%20Sunday%20and%20then%20Egytian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20in%20Cairo%2C%20where%20he%20received%20a%20blunt%20assessment%20from%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20of%20Israel's%20response%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20that%20killed%201%2C300%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20(Israeli)%20reaction%20went%20beyond%20the%20right%20to%20self-defence%2C%20turning%20into%20collective%20punishment%20for%202.3%20million%20people%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20told%20Blinken%20in%20televised%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20annihilate%20Hamas%20-%20which%20controls%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20-%20after%20its%20fighters%20stormed%20Israeli%20towns%20eight%20days%20ago%2C%20shooting%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20and%20seizing%20hostages%20in%20the%20worst%20attack%20on%20civilians%20in%20the%20country's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20jets%20and%20artillery%20have%20already%20subjected%20Gaza%20to%20the%20most%20intense%20bombardment%20it%20has%20ever%20seen%2C%20putting%20the%20enclave%20under%20total%20siege.%20Gaza%20authorities%20say%20more%20than%202%2C450%20people%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20ACTS%20TO%20DETER%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInternational%20diplomacy%20has%20been%20focused%20on%20preventing%20a%20spill%20over%20of%20the%20conflict%20-%20particularly%20into%20Lebanon.%20The%20United%20States%20has%20been%20specifically%20trying%20to%20deter%20Iran%2C%20which%20backs%20Hamas%20and%20Lebanon's%20Hezbollah%20group.%20Hezbollah%20and%20Israel%20have%20already%20been%20exchanging%20border%20fire%20over%20the%20past%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20said%20the%20United%20States%20had%20made%20clear%20that%20state%20and%20non-state%20actors%20should%20not%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20backed%20up%20those%20words%20with%20concrete%20actions%2C%20including%20the%20deployment%20now%20of%20our%20two%20largest%20aircraft%20carrier%20battle%20groups%20to%20the%20region.%20That's%20not%20meant%20as%20a%20provocation%2C%20it's%20meant%20as%20a%20deterrent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20should%20do%20anything%20that%20could%20add%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%20in%20any%20other%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20departing%20for%20Cairo%2C%20Blinken%20described%20his%20talks%20with%20the%20Saudi%20crown%20prince%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20leaders%20of%20the%20region%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20productive.%26quot%3B%20A%20US%20official%20said%20the%20meeting%20lasted%20for%20just%20under%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20crown%20prince%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20stop%20the%20conflict%2C%20and%20respect%20international%20law%2C%20including%20by%20lifting%20the%20Israeli%20blockade%20on%20Gaza%2C%20Saudi%20state%20news%20agency%20SPA%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20said%20in%20Cairo%20that%20the%20Rafah%20crossing%20between%20Egypt%20and%20Gaza%20would%20reopen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20very%20actively%20engaged%20with%20countries%20in%20the%20region%2C%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20with%20Israel%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20to%20the%20best%20of%20our%20ability%20that%20people%20can%20get%20out%20of%20harm's%20way%20and%20that%20the%20assistance%20they%20need%2C%20the%20food%20and%20water%20and%20medicine%2C%20can%20get%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697414220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fvtg5ccag_antony-blinken_625x300_09_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Farab-states-determined-to-not-let-israel-hamas-war-spread-antony-blinken-4484205%22%2C%22s