%20food.%20All%20goods%20are%20not%20available%20and%20the%20costs%20of%20what%20is%20available%20have%20surged.%20The%20only%20foods%20we%20find%20are%20tuna%20cans%20and%20cheese.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20a%20burden%2C%20unable%20to%20do%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20estimates%20that%20about%20one%20million%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20since%20Israel%20began%20a%20relentless%20aerial%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20in%20retaliation%20for%20Hamas's%20deadly%20assault%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas%20attack%20left%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people%20dead%20on%20the%20Israeli%20side%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Gazan%20side%2C%20at%20least%202%2C670%20have%20died%20in%20the%20relentless%20bombing%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20ordinary%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20also%20cut%20off%20all%20water%2C%20electricity%20and%20food%20supplies%20to%20the%20densely-populated%20coastal%20enclave%2C%20before%20resuming%20water%20to%20the%20south%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMona%20Abdel%20Hamid%2C%2055%2C%20left%20her%20home%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20heading%20for%20her%20relatives'%20house%20in%20Rafah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20in%20the%20home%20of%20people%20she%20did%20not%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20humiliation%20and%20embarrassment.%20I'm%20looking%20for%20refuge.%20We%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20clothes%20and%20most%20of%20them%20are%20dirty%20now%2C%20with%20no%20water%20to%20wash%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20electricity%2C%20no%20water%2C%20no%20internet.%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20losing%20my%20humanity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E-%20'Lives%20in%20displacement'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Friday%2C%20Sabah%20Masbah%2C%2050%2C%20has%20lived%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20daughter%20and%2021%20other%20relatives%20at%20a%20friend's%20home%20in%20Rafah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20worst%20and%20most%20dangerous%20thing%20is%20that%20we%20can't%20find%20water.%20None%20of%20us%20bathe%20now%20because%20the%20water%20is%20so%20scarce%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20home%20in%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20near%20a%20school%20run%20by%20the%20UN%20agency%20supporting%20Palestinian%20refugees%2C%20Esam%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20received%20guests%20who%20were%20displaced%20from%20the%20Gaza%20City%20area%2C%20the%20Al-Rimal%20neighbourhood%20and%20Tal%20al-Hawa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bwater%20is%20a%20problem%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%2023-year-old%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20give%20his%20full%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20day%20we%20think%20of%20how%20to%20get%20water...%20If%20we%20bathe%2C%20we%20won't%20drink.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20have%20sought%20refuge%20at%20the%20UNRWA%20schools%20also%20desperately%20seek%20food%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20agency's%20director%20of%20communications%2C%20Juliette%20Touma%2C%20told%20AFP%20more%20people%20are%20likely%20to%20become%20displaced%20%26quot%3Bas%20people%20continue%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20massing%20forces%20and%20weapons%20at%20the%20border%20with%20Gaza%20ahead%20of%20an%20expected%20ground%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Israeli%20evacuation%20order%2C%20there%20were%20air%20strikes%20in%20the%20south%2C%20including%20in%20Rafah%2C%20where%20one%20resident%20said%20a%20doctor's%20house%20was%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20family%20was%20wiped%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khamis%20Abu%20Hilal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlaa%20al-Hams%20pointed%20to%20the%20fresh%20signs%20of%20shelling%20on%20a%20neighbourhood%20in%20Rafah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20at%20the%20massive%20destruction.%20They%20say%20there%20is%20terrorism%20here.%20Where%20is%20the%20humanity%20they%20speak%20of%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20are%20civilians%20here%2C%20with%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20any%20organisations%2C%20but%20they%20died...%20no%20one%20is%20left%20alive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESamira%20Kassab%20stands%20on%20the%20remains%20of%20what%20was%20once%20her%20home%20in%20Rafah%2C%20asking%3A%20%26quot%3BWhere%20will%20we%20go%3F%20Where%20are%20the%20Arab%20countries%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20spent%20our%20whole%20lives%20in%20displacement.%20Our%20home%2C%20which%20housed%20all%20my%20children%2C%20was%20struck...%20We%20slept%20in%20the%20street%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20isolated.%20My%20daughter%20has%20cancer%20and%20I%20can't%20take%20her%20to%20the%20hospital.%20I%20myself%20suffer%20from%20hypertension%20and%20diabetes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20defiantly%20raised%20the%20victory%20sign%20with%20her%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20her%20grandchildren%20she%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20won't%20leave%20no%20matter%20what%2C%20even%20if%20I%20die.%20We%20beg%20for%20bread%20from%20our%20neighbours%2C%20but%20we%20will%20not%20part%20with%20a%20grain%20of%20sand.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697407620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F9cmv5j1_gaza-reuters_625x300_15_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fif-we-bathe-we-wont-drink-gazans-struggle-with-dwindling-water-supply-4484168%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20scores%20of%20people%20line%20up%20at%20bathrooms%2C%20many%20of%20them%20not%20having%20showered%20for%20days%20after%20Israel%20cut%20off%20water%2C%20electricity%20an