Afghanistan%20not%20known%20for%20seismic%20activity%20was%20struck%20by%20an%20'unprecedented'%20number%20of%20big%20earthquakes%20this%20week%20and%20no%20one%20knows%20when%20they'll%20end%2C%20an%20expert%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225527%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20tents%20that%20residents%20of%20Herat%20are%20sleeping%20in%20to%20avoid%20buildings%20that%20could%20collapse%20in%20future%20earthquakes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652c311c55f52b01b35fe87e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223685%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThousands%20of%20people%20living%20in%20Herat%20are%20now%20sleeping%20in%20tents%20to%20stay%20safe%20from%20buildings%20that%20could%20collapse%20in%20future%20quakes.%3Cp%3EEsmatullah%20Habibian%2FMiddle%20East%20Images%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWestern%20Afghanistan%20has%20been%20struck%20by%20four%20major%20earthquakes%20in%20just%20over%20a%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20researcher%20with%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20said%20these%20earthquakes%20are%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUnsure%20when%20they'll%20end%2C%20Afghan%20residents%20are%20living%20in%20tents%20to%20avoid%20collapsing%20buildings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20Afghanistan%20was%20struck%20by%20yet%20another%20powerful%20earthquake%20on%20Sunday%2C%20its%20fourth%20in%20just%20over%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESunday's%20earthquakes%20came%20in%20at%206.3%20and%205.4%20magnitudes%2C%20with%20the%20epicenter%20just%2020%20miles%20outside%20Herat%20City%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F15%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fafghanistan-earthquakes-again.html%3Futm_source%3Dpocket_saves%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%201%2C300%20people%20were%20killed%20by%20the%20initial%206.3%20magnitude%20earthquake%20on%20October%207.%20Another%201%2C700%20were%20injured.%20A%20fourth%20major%20earthquake%20struck%20the%20region%20on%20October%2011.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20week%2C%20Herat%20Province%20residents%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20unsure%20when%20the%20tremors%20will%20cease%20%E2%80%94%20have%20fled%20the%20region%20or%20moved%20into%20tents%20to%20avoid%20collapsing%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20series%20of%20major%20earthquakes%20is%20unprecedented%20for%20the%20region%2C%20according%20to%20William%20Barnhart%2C%20assistant%20coordinator%20for%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20Earthquake%20Hazards%20Program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20very%20little%20precedent%20for%20a%20sequence%20like%20this%20where%20you%20have%20four%20earthquakes%20of%20the%20same%20magnitude%20in%20a%20week%2C%20and%20even%20less%20precedence%20in%20this%20part%20of%20Afghanistan%20where%2C%20to%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20there's%20just%20no%20history%20of%20damage%20and%20earthquakes%20in%20and%20around%20Herat%2C%26quot%3B%20Barnhart%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20makes%20these%20quakes%20especially%20dangerous%20for%20residents%20of%20Herat.%20Buildings%20and%20infrastructure%20tend%20to%20be%20vulnerable%20in%20regions%20that%20aren't%20prone%20to%20earthquakes%2C%20Barnhart%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarthquakes%20of%20this%20frequency%20and%20size%20following%20an%20initial%206.3-magnitude%20quake%20are%20rare%20almost%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20looking%20through%20statistics%20and%20I%20haven't%20found%20instances%20of%20this%20except%20for%20cases%20in%20volcanically%20active%20regions%20or%20in%20aftershock%20sequences%20of%20much%20bigger%20earthquakes%2C%26quot%3B%20Barnhart%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20neither%20of%20those%20scenarios%20apply%20to%20this%20ongoing%20earthquake%20sequence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Barnhart%20said%20it's%20unlikely%20the%20region%20will%20experience%2