arlie-javice-frank-criminal-charges-financial-fraud-jpmorgan-chase-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4.25%20million%20users%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20bank%20claims%20the%20platform%20never%20had%20more%20than%20about%20250%2C000%2C%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrank-founder-charlie-javice-arraigned-on-fraud-charges-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJavice%20fabricated%20these%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20providing%20the%20bank%20with%20millions%20of%20student%20names%20and%20emails%20that%20were%20%26quot%3Ball%20fake%2C%26quot%3B%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Insider%20investigation%20found%20that%20Javice%20had%20a%20pattern%20of%20exaggerating%20her%20successes%20throughout%20her%20career.%20In%20particular%2C%20she%20misrepresented%20the%20fact%20that%20her%20company%20could%20double%20the%20amount%20of%20aid%20students%20received%20by%20helping%20them%20fill%20out%20the%20Free%20Application%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20(FAFSA)%20form%2C%20student%20financial%20aid%20expert%20Mark%20Kantrowitz%20previously%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrank%20did%20nothing%20that%20would%20have%20affected%20the%20amount%20of%20aid%20the%20students%20would%20have%20received%20had%20they%20filed%20the%20FAFSA%20on%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Kantrowitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20not%20have%20led%20to%20a%20doubling%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20financial%20aid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Justice%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider%20ahead%20of%20publication.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-frank-jp-morgan-fraud-case-witholding-documents-slack-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697389038000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652c0e6455f52b01b35fe1be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-frank-jp-morgan-fraud-case-witholding-documents-slack-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Charlie%20Javice%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20student%20aid%20startup%20Frank%2C%20is%20facing%20criminal%20charges%20after%20JP%20Morgan%20said%20she%20defrauded%20them%20out%20of%20%24175%20million.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22khawkinson%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Hawkinson%20%2CJack%20Newsham)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-frank-jp-morgan-fraud-case-witholding-documents-slack-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20Cup%202023%3A%20Afghanistan%20Stun%20England%20In%20Battle%20Of%20David%20vs%20Goliath%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%20pulled%20off%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20upsets%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20after%20they%20beat%20defending%20champions%20England%20by%2069%20runs%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0Afghanistan%20thus%20registered%20their%20first%20win%20over%20England%20in%20One-Day%20Internationals.%20Flamboyant%20opening%20batsman%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahmanullah%20Gurbaz%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F111914-rahmanullah-gurbaz-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahmanullah%20Gurbaz%3C%2Fa%3E%20hit%20a%20blistering%2080%20as%20Afghanistan%2C%20buoyed%20by%20some%20lusty%20late%20hitting%2C%20made%20284%20batting%20first.%20In%20reply%2C%20Rashid%20Khan%20and%20Mujeeb-ur-Rahman%20bagged%20three%20wickets%20a%20to%20help%20Afghanistan%20roll%20over%20England%20on%20a%20total%20of%20215.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20was%20Afghanistan's%20first%20win%20in%20the%20ongoing%20tournament%20after%20two%20losses%2C%20England%20slumped%20to%20their%20second%20defeat%20from%20three%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERashid%20Khan%20(3%2F37)%20and%20Mujeeb%20Ur%20Rahman%20(3%2F51)%20were%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20Afghan%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHarry%20Brook%20(66%20off%2061)%20was%20the%20only%20shining%20light%20in%20what%20was%20a%20dismal%20batting%20display%20from%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECredit%20should%20also%20go%20to%20former%20England%20batter%20Jonathan%20Trott%2C%20who%20is%20the%20present%20Afghanistan%20coach%2C%20for%20having%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20team's%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngland%20did%20not%20have%20the%20best%20of%20starts%20to%20their%20chase%20with%20Fazalhaq%20Farooqi%20inflicting%20an%20early%20blow%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Jonny%20Bairstow%2C%20who%20was%20caught%20plumb%20in%20front%20of%20the%20wicket%20in%20the%20second%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFarooqi%20generated%20pace%20and%20troubled%20the%20English%20batters%20in%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Kotla%20pitch%20also%20had%20something%20for%20the%20spinners%20as%20the%20ball%20kept%20low%20and%20turned%20under%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20in-form%20Joe%20Root%2C%20who%20had%20scored%20back-to-back%20fifties%2C%20was%20done%20in%20by%20a%20Mujeeb%20delivery%20that%20kept%20low%20and%20crashed%20onto%20the%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDawis%20Malan%20played%20cautiously%20for%20his%2032%20off%2039%20balls%20before%20handing%20a%20simple%20catch%20to%20Ibrahim%20Zadran%20at%20short%20extra%20cover%20off%20Mohammad%20Nabi%2C%20as%20England%20stuttered%20to%2068%20for%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngland%20completely%20failed%20to%20judge%20the%20pitch%20as%20their%20decision%20to%20bowl%20first%20backfired%20with%20the%20pitch%20offering%20enough%20assistance%20to%20the%20bowlers%20in%20the%20second%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Jos%20Buttler%20also%20failed%20to%20rescue%20his%20side%20as%20he%20was%20cleaned%20up%20by%20Naveen-ul-Haq%20with%20a%20delivery%20that%20came%20in%20after%20pitching.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngland%20continued%20to%20lose%20wickets%20in%20regular%20intervals%20as%20Liam%20Livingstone%2C%20Sam%20Curran%20and%20Chris%20Woakes%20also%20failed%20with%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20opener%20Gurbaz%20gave%20the%20Afghans%20a%20flying%20start%2C%20scoring%2080%20off%2057%20balls%2C%20while%20number%206%20batter%20Alikhil%20made%20a%20solid%2058%20off%2066%20deliveries%2C%20as%20Afghanistan%20recovered%20from%20a%20mid-innings%20collapse%20to%20post%20a%20good%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOff-colour%20in%20the%20first%20two%20matches%2C%20Afghanistan%20openers%20--%20Gurbaz%20and%20Ibrahim%20Zadran%20(28)%20--%20rose%20to%20the%20occasion%2C%20scoring%20the%20team's%2050%20in%20just%206.3%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghan%20openers%20meant%20business%20and%20played%20copybook%20shots%20to%20score%20their%20runs.%20The%20duo%20didn't%20take%20too%20many%20risks%20and%20Gurbaz%20mainly%20ruled%20the%20roost%2C%20taking%20the%20attack%20to%20the%20English%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20played%20all%20around%20the%20park%20and%20his%20shots%20through%20the%20covers%20and%20flicks%20were%20a%20treat%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Afghanistan%20scoring%20runs%20thick%20and%20fast%2C%20Buttler%20introduced%20Adil%20Rashid%20(3%2F42)%20in%20the%2011th%20over%20but%20Gurbaz%20was%20in%20a%20relentless%20mood%20as%20he%20swept%20the%20leg-spinner%20for%20a%20boundary%20to%20bring%20up%20his%20fifty%20in%20just%2033%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGurbaz%20looked%20in%20ominous%20form%20as%20he%20dispatched%20Rashid%20over%20deep%20midwicket%20to%20bring%20up%20Afghanistan's%20100%20in%20just%2076%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngland%20tasted%20their%20first%20success%20in%20the%2017th%20over%20when%20an%20under-pressure%20Zadran%20(28%20off%2048%20balls)%20gave%20a%20simple%20catch%20to%20Root%20at%20short%20mid%20wicket%20but%20not%20before%20adding%20114%20runs%20for%20the%20opening%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngland%20got%20back%20into%20the%20g