ws%2Fflipkart-witnesses-record-visits-of-1-4-bn-customer-during-tbbd-sale-123101500670_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fflipkart-witnesses-record-visits-of-1-4-bn-customer-during-tbbd-sale-123101500670_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Gaza%20Deaths%20Rise%2C%20Ice%20Cream%20Trucks%20Double%20Up%20As%20Morgues%20For%20Bodies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHealth%20officials%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%20Strip%20have%20resorted%20to%20storing%20the%20bodies%20of%20Palestinians%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20in%20ice%20cream%20freezer%20trucks%20because%20moving%20them%20to%20hospitals%20is%20too%20risky%20and%20cemeteries%20are%20short%20of%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20unleashed%20the%20fiercest%20bombardment%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20to%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%20after%20it%20carried%20out%20the%20deadliest%20attack%20on%20Israel%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hospital%20morgue%20can%20only%20take%2010%20bodies%2C%20so%20we%20have%20brought%20in%20ice%20cream%20freezers%20from%20the%20ice%20cream%20factories%20in%20order%20to%20store%20the%20huge%20numbers%20of%20martyrs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr.%20Yasser%20Ali%20of%20the%20Shuhada%20Al-Aqsa%20hospital%20in%20Deir%20Al-Balah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20freezer%20trucks%2C%20whose%20sides%20still%20show%20advertising%20images%20of%20smiling%20children%20enjoying%20ice%20cream%20cones%2C%20are%20normally%20used%20to%20make%20deliveries%20to%20supermarkets.%20Now%20they%20are%20makeshift%20morgues%20for%20victims%20of%20the%20devastating%20war%20between%20Hamas%20and%20the%20Israeli%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20on%20Sunday%20it%20would%20still%20allow%20Gazans%20to%20evacuate%20south%20ahead%20of%20an%20expected%20ground%20assault%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20attacks%20by%20eight%20days%20ago%20by%20Hamas%20gunmen%2C%20who%20killed%201%2C300%20people%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20in%20Gaza%20said%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20had%20killed%20more%20than%202%2C300%20people%2C%20a%20quarter%20of%20them%20children%2C%20with%20nearly%2010%2C000%20wounded%20so%20far.%20Hospitals%20are%20running%20short%20of%20supplies%20and%20struggling%20to%20cope%20with%20growing%20numbers%20of%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20annihilate%20Hamas%20after%20its%20fighters%20rampaged%20through%20Israeli%20towns%20on%20Oct.%207%20shooting%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20and%20seizing%20hostages.%20That%20means%20the%20Gaza%20death%20count%20will%20rise%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20with%20these%20freezers%2C%20the%20number%20(of%20the%20dead)%20exceeds%20the%20capacity%20of%20this%20main%20morgue%20of%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20alternative%20ones%2C%20and%20between%2020%20and%2030%20bodies%20are%20being%20kept%20in%20tents%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ali%2C%20as%20he%20opened%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20freezers%20to%20show%20the%20white-shrouded%20bodies%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Gaza%20Strip%20is%20in%20crisis%20and%20if%20the%20war%20continues%20in%20this%20way%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20bury%20the%20dead.%20The%20cemeteries%20are%20already%20full%20and%20we%20need%20new%20ones%20to%20bury%20the%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20Ali%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%20City%20too%2C%20authorities%20were%20preparing%20mass%20graves%2C%20said%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Government%20Media%20Office%2C%20Salama%20Marouf.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20light%20of%20the%20large%20number%20of%20martyrs%20inside%20the%20morgues%20of%20Al-Shifa%20Hospital%2C%20whose%20relatives%20did%20not%20arrive%20to%20bury%20them%2C%20signs%20of%20change%20began%20to%20appear%20on%20the%20bodies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20in%20light%20of%20the%20continued%20arrival%20of%20martyrs%20in%20their%20dozens%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20occupation's%20massacres%2C%20a%20mass%20grave%20has%20been%20prepared%20to%20bury%20approximately%20100%20martyrs%20in%20the%20emergency%20cemetery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697381760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fled6s65_gaza-ice-cream-trucks-as-morgues-reuters_625x300_15_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-gaza-deaths-rise-ice-cream-trucks-double-up-as-morgues-for-bodies-4483692%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Health%20officials%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%20Strip%20have%20resorted%20to%20storing%20the%20bodies%20of%20Palestinians%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20in%20ice%20cream%20freezer%20trucks%20because%20moving%20them%20to%20hospitals%20is%20too%20risky%20and%20cemeteries%20are%20short%20of%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-gaza-deaths-rise-ice-cream-trucks-double-up-as-morgues-for-bodies-4483692%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-gaza-deaths-rise-ice-cream-trucks-double-up-as-morgues-for-bodies-4483692%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-gaza-deaths-rise-ice-cream-trucks-double-up-as-morgues-for-bodies-4483692%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Repos%20Energy%20to%20raise%20Rs%20100-300%20cr%20in%20Series%20A%20funding%20by%20June%20next%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697381172000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-08%2F21%2Ffull%2F1661101398-4467.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Frepos-energy-to-raise-r