in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20public%20event%20in%20Jammu%20on%20October%2014%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyexcelsior.com%2Fanti-india-separatist-corrupt-ecosystems-worried-in-jk-lg%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20reported%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Excelsior%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sinha%20%E2%80%9Creferred%20to%20a%20news%20item%20pertaining%20to%20AB-PMJAY%20Sehat%20Scheme%20and%20said%20writer%20of%20the%20article%20was%20himself%20an%20active%20part%20of%20separatist%20ecosystem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20founding%20editor%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%20says%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%20accusation%E2%80%9D%20coming%20from%20the%20LG%E2%80%99s%20high%20office%20could%20have%20perilous%20consequences%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20the%20journalist%20you%20are%20targeting%20and%20also%20for%20the%20media%20more%20broadly%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmong%20other%20things%2C%20it%20suggests%20a%20willingness%20on%20the%20part%20of%20your%20administration%20to%20interfere%20with%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20freedom%20of%20the%20press.%20A%20journalist%20has%20and%20exercises%20these%20rights%20not%20only%20in%20his%20or%20her%20personal%20capacity%2C%20but%20also%20because%20citizens%20at%20large%20have%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20a%20range%20of%20news%20and%20views%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20requested%20Sinha%20to%20withdraw%20the%20accusation%20against%20Jehangir%20Ali%20and%20refrain%20from%20making%20such%20%E2%80%9Cunfounded%20allegations%20against%20bona%20fide%20members%20of%20the%20media%2C%20which%20is%20a%20crucial%20pillar%20of%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20letter%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E15.10.2023%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lt.%20Governor%20Sinha%2C%3Cbr%3E%20Raj%20Bhavan%3Cbr%3E%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDear%20Lt%20Governor%20Sinha%3Cbr%3E%20Subject%3A%20Your%20remarks%20as%20reported%20in%20Daily%20Excelsior%20on%20October%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20am%20writing%20to%20you%20as%20the%20Founding%20Editor%20of%20The%20Wire%20to%20protest%20your%20unwarranted%20and%20unacceptable%20description%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwriter%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20news%20article%20on%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri-Jan%20Arogya%20Yojna%20insurance%20scheme%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20an%20active%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cseparatist%20ecosystem%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20also%20cross-checked%20what%20the%20Daily%20Excelsior%20quoted%20you%20as%20saying%20against%20a%20video%20recording%20of%20your%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20article%20in%20question%20was%20published%20in%20The%20Wire%20and%20the%20writer%20concerned%2C%20Jehangir%20Ali%2C%20has%20been%20a%20correspondent%20of%20The%20Wire%20for%20several%20years%20now%2C%20filing%20regular%20reports%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20Jehangir%20Ali%20has%20ever%20written%20for%20The%20Wire%20or%20elsewhere%20that%20justifies%20the%20accusation%20levelled%20by%20you.%20And%20one%20would%20be%20hard%20put%20to%20find%20anything%20that%20he%20has%20ever%20done%2C%20to%20justify%20it%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20baseless%20accusation%20coming%20from%20the%20high%20office%20that%20you%20hold%20has%20perilous%20consequences%20for%20the%20journalist%20you%20are%20targeting%20and%20also%20for%20the%20media%20more%20broadly.%20Among%20other%20things%2C%20it%20suggests%20a%20willingness%20on%20the%20part%20of%20your%20administration%20to%20interfere%20with%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20freedom%20of%20the%20press.%20A%20journalist%20has%20and%20exercises%20these%20rights%20not%20only%20in%20his%20or%20her%20personal%20capacity%2C%20but%20also%20because%20citizens%20at%20large%20have%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20a%20range%20of%20news%20and%20views.%20As%20you%20might%20be%20aware%2C%20this%20position%20has%20been%20recognised%20as%20a%20basic%20constitutional%20principle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20in%20question%20is%20a%20discussion%20on%20policy%20and%20lies%20fully%20within%20the%20realm%20of%20legitimate%20expression.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20government%20has%20the%20right%20to%20differ%20or%20issue%20a%20factual%20rejoinder%20if%20it%20wishes.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20The%20Wire%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20publish%20the%20same%20should%20you%20care%20to%20formally%20issue%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20should%2C%20however%2C%20be%20obvious%20that%20criticism%20of%20government%20policy%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20separatism.%20Equally%2C%20that%20publicly%20branding%20a%20journalist%20whose%20news%20report%20the%20government%20disapproves%20of%20as%20%E2%80%98separatist%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20your%20right%20to%20issue%20a%20formal%20rejoinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20request%20you%20to%20withdraw%20your%20accusation%20against%20Jehangir%20Ali%20and%20refrain%20from%20making%20such%20unfounded%20allegations%20against%20bona%20fide%20members%20of%20the%20media%2C%20which%20is%20a%20crucial%20pillar%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYours%20sincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESiddharth%20Varadarajan%3Cbr%3E%20Founding%20Editor%3Cbr%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697366424000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F15160522%2FF28AVhZaUAARAph.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-wire-jammu-and-kashmir-lg-separatist-ecosystem-charge-correspondent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20letter%2C%20The%20Wire%20told%20LG%20Manoj%20Sinha%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20accusation%26quot%3B%20against%20Jehangir%20Ali%2C%20for%20a%20story%20on%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri-Jan%20Arogya%2