80%99s%20%3Cem%3EDumb%20Money%3C%2Fem%3E%20reminds%20you%20of%20David%20Fincher%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlB95KLmpLR4%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Social%20Network%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E(2010)%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20good%20reasons%20for%20it.%20Apart%20from%20Will%20Bates%E2%80%99%20electro-synth%20score%20(reminiscent%20of%20Trent%20Reznor%20%26amp%3B%20Atticus%20Ross%E2%80%99%20Oscar-winning%20score%20in%20Fincher%E2%80%99s%20film%2C)%20and%20principal%20characters%20staring%20at%20computer%20screens%20for%20a%20large%20part%20of%20its%20107-minute%20runtime%2C%20%3Cem%3EDumb%20Money%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20based%20on%20Ben%20Mezrich%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FANTISOCIAL-NETWORK-Ben-Mezrich%2Fdp%2F1538707551%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Antisocial%20Network%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2021).%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20same%20author%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FAccidental-Billionaires-Founding-Facebook-Betrayal%2Fdp%2F0307740986%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Accidental%20Billionaires%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(2009)%20served%20as%20the%20source%20material%20for%20the%20Fincher-Sorkin%20classic.%20Another%20probably%20inconsequential%20detail%20is%20that%20the%202023%20film%E2%80%99s%20executive%20producers%20are%20Cameron%20and%20Tyler%20Winklevoss%20%E2%80%93%20who%2C%20some%20might%20label%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98antagonists%E2%80%99%20from%20Mezrich%E2%80%99s%202009%20book.%20This%20is%20where%20the%20similarities%20end%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGillespie%E2%80%99s%20film%20%E2%80%93%20charting%20the%20%E2%80%98GameStop%20saga%E2%80%99%20from%20late%202020%20to%20early%202021%2C%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic%20in%20America%20%E2%80%93%20is%20closer%20to%20Adam%20McKay%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Big%20Short%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2016)%20and%20Gillespie%E2%80%99s%20own%20%3Cem%3EI%2C%20Tonya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2017)%20in%20tone.%20It%20has%20light%20feet%2C%20a%20colourful%20soundtrack%2C%20a%20frothy%20narrative%2C%20and%20an%20eye-popping%20ensemble%20%E2%80%93%20telling%20us%20about%20a%20rare%20time%20when%20Wall%20Street%E2%80%99s%20own%20severely%20compromised%20system%20was%20weaponised%20against%20them%20by%20some%20rag-tag%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20hysterical%20headline%20describes%20the%20saga%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CFrench%20Revolution%20of%20the%20stock%20market%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20hyperbole%20that%20cuts%20through%20the%20social%20media%20noise%20these%20days.%20How%20do%20you%20mean%20a%20billion-dollar%20hedge%20fund%20had%20to%20shut%20shop%20because%20of%20a%20movement%20fuelled%20by%20gifs%20and%20memes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fbmr8YmwnZ3w%3Fsi%3DjOvaox62QXbZSOrb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EKeith%20Gill%20(Paul%20Dano)%20is%2C%20for%20all%20intents%20and%20purposes%2C%20what%20we%20can%20call%20%E2%80%98a%20work-in-progress%E2%80%99%20(a%20polite%20word%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98loser%E2%80%99).%20He%20began%20his%20career%20as%20stock%20market%20analyst%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202008%20stock%20market%20crash%2C%20and%20since%20then%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20anything%20steady.%20After%20several%20short%20stints%20in%20major%20investment%20banks%2C%20Gill%20is%20now%20in%20a%20modest%20job%2C%20and%20he%20likes%20to%20fill%20his%20time%20doling%20out%20advice%20for%20amateur%20investors%20through%20a%20YouTube%20livestream.%20He%20hosts%20these%20streams%20on%20a%20Reddit%20thread%20called%20r%2FWallStreetBets%2C%20under%20the%20username%20RoaringKitty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20on%20these%20Vlogs%20that%20Gill%20mentions%20being%20bullish%20on%20a%20stock%20called%20GameStop%20%E2%80%93%20a%20company%20that%20makes%20gaming%20equipment.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Melvin%20Capital%2C%20a%20Wall%20Street%20hedge%20fund%20owned%20by%20Gabe%20Plotkin%20(Seth%20Rogen)%2C%20is%20bracing%20itself%20to%20downsize%20the%20company%20%E2%80%93%20given%20its%20stagnant%20revenue%2C%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20promise%20or%20an%20upward%20movement%2C%20according%20to%20Wall%20Street.%20Gill%20puts%20all%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20savings%20into%20the%20stock%20(~%2450%2C000).%20As%20some%20people%20start%20to%20listen%20to%20him%2C%20the%20value%20of%20the%20stock%20begins%20to%20rise%20and%20word%20spreads%20around%20that%20buying%20GameStop%20might%20yield%20good%20returns%20in%20the%20short%20term%20%E2%80%93%20encouraging%20people%20to%20buy%20more%20of%20the%20stock.%20At%20this%20stage%2C%20the%20value%20of%20the%20stock%20starts%20to%20increase%20and%20the%20more%20this%20happens%2C%20the%20more%20Wall%20Street%20hedge%20funds%20stand%20to%20lose%2C%20because%20of%20their%20obligation%20to%20cover%20their%20short%20positions%20on%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20starts%20off%20as%20one%20man%E2%80%99s%20hunch%20about%20a%20stock%2C%20slowly%20becomes%20a%20movement%20on%20social%20media%20against%20the%20top%200.1%25.%20The%20retail%20investors%2C%20dubbed%20%E2%80%9CDumb%20Money%E2%80%9D%20by%20market%20players%20for%20being%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20their%20manipulations%2C%20can%20be%20seen%20hunting%20down%20the%20so-called%20lions.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20glorious%20once-in-a-lifetime%20event%2C%20when%20the%20stars%20align%20in%20a%20manner%20allowing%20justice%20to%20prevail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDumb%20Money%3C%2Fem%3E%20features%20cosy%2C%20efficient%20performances%20especially%20by%20Paul%20Dano%20as%20Keith%20Gill%2C%20who%20nails%20the%20dorky%20%E2%80%98influencer%E2%80%99%20type%2C%20who%20wears%20cat%20t-shirts%20and%20a%20red%20bandana%20on%20his%20streams.%20But%20he%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20real%20person%20who%20seems%20to%20know%20some%20of%20the%20things%20he%E2%80%99s%20talking%20about.%20Dano%E2%80%99s%20performance%20is%20a%20delicate%20dance%20%E2%80%93%20tipping%20one%20way%20or%20another%2C%20it%20could%20have%20either%20ended%20up%20looking%20like%20a%20caricature%20or%20sucked%20all%20the%20fun%20out%20of%20the%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDano%20is%20surrounded%20by%20an%20excellent%20cast%20including%20Shailene%20Woodley%2C%20Anthony%20Ramos%2C%20America%20Ferrera%2C%20Pete%20Davidson%2C%20Sebastian%20Stan%2C%20Rogen%2C%20Vincent%20D%E2%80%99Onofrio%2C%20Dane%20De%20Haan%20and%20Nick%20Offerman.%20Except%20Dano%2C%20none%20of%20the%20other%20characters%20are%20well-defined%2C%20but%20it%20never%20becomes%20burdensome%20to%20watch%20them%20turn%20in%20effortless%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20value%20of%20the%20stock%20rises%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Gill%E2%80%99s%20%2450%2C000-dollar%20investment%20balloons%20into%20%2450%20million%2C%20that%20is%20when%20the%20conflict%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20moment%20the%20buyers%20sell%20the%20stocks%2C%20the%20hedge%20funds%20stop%20bleeding%20losses.%20Multiple%20characters%20%E2%80%93%20all%20denoted%20on%20the%20screen%20in%20Wall%20Street%20lingo%20by%20their%20%E2%80%9Cnet%20worth%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20wrestle%20with%20whether%20they%20should%20sell.%20These%20include%20underpaid%20nurses%20%E2%80%93%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20a%20dentist%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20for%20their%20children%20%E2%80%93%20college%20students%20with%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20debt%2C%20and%20people%20like%20Gill%2C%20who%20have%20undergone%20a%20lifetime%20of%20a%20grind%20just%20to%20have%20a%20shot%20at%20a%20silver%20lining%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20lobbies%20pull%20around%20their%20weight%20to%20break%20this%20Internet%20movement%2C%20by%20shutting%20down%20the%20message%20board%20where%20Gill%20used%20to%20communicate%20with%20his%20followers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20manipulating%20the%20application%20(called%20Robinhood)%20used%20by%20the%20retail%20investors%20to%20buy%20the%20GameStop%20stock%20%E2%80%93%20leading%20to%20an%20air%20of%20distrust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGillespie%E2%80%99s%20film%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20wade%20too%20deep%20into%20the%20well-known%20systemic%20rot%20of%20Wall%20Street%2C%20keeping%20the%20film%20as%20accessible%20as%20possible.%20So%2C%20on%20one%20level%20while%20the%20film%20remains%20immensely%20watchable%2C%20it%20also%20never%20really%20addresses%20how%20this%20was%20a%20black%20swan%20event%20%E2%80%93%20unlikely%20to%20ever%20be%20repeated%20in%20the%20next%20few%20decades%20at%20least.%20So%20improbable%20are%20these%20chain%20of%20events%20that%20in%20retrospect%20it%20makes%20it%20almost%20seem%20like%20a%20miracle%20that%20it%20happened%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDumb%20Money%3C%2Fem%3E%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20educate.%20It%20wants%20to%20reflect%20on%20a%20rare%20moment%20when%20people%20came%20together%20in%20the%20first%20world%2C%20on%20a%20platform%20(the%20Internet)%20that%20isn%E2%80%99t%20even%20taken%20seriously%20by%20most%2C%20to%20effect%20some%20real-world%20change.%20I%20wonder%20what%20those%20who%20invented%20the%20Internet%20%E2%80%93%20a%20place%20initially%20for%20introverts%20to%20whisper%20their%20theories%20about%20the%20world%20on%20anonymous%20message%20boards%2C%20suddenly%20taken%20over%20by%20extroverts%20thanks%20to%20social%20media%20%E2%80%93%20have%20to%20say%20about%20this%20event%20shaking%20up%20the%20status-quo%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20damning%20evidence%20that%20when%20sincere%2C%20like-minded%20people%20come%20together%2C%20they%20can%20take%20down%20the%20most%20ruthless%2C%20oppressive%20systems.%20Anyone%20can%20be%20a%20hero%20%E2%80%93%20even%20someone%20populating%20his%20streams%20with%20enough%20cat%20gifs%20and%20memes.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20kind%20of%20hope%20we%20need%20in%20times%20like%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A169736044500