%2C%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20and%20its%20HR%20head%2C%20Amit%20Chakravarty%2C%20were%20arrested%20under%20charges%20of%20terrorism%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%20by%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%20This%20happened%20after%20the%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-raids-journos-questioned-delhi-riots-farmers-protest-covid-crisis%5C%22%3Eraided%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%2070%20locations%20connected%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20including%20the%20homes%20of%20its%20employees%2C%20contributors%2C%20and%20consultants.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECIVICUS%20is%20a%20global%20alliance%20%E2%80%9Cof%20over%2010%2C000%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20activists%20dedicated%20to%20strengthening%20citizen%20action%20and%20civil%20society%20throughout%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20complete%20assault%20on%20press%20freedom%20in%20India%20and%20an%20act%20of%20reprisal%20against%20the%20critical%20and%20independent%20journalism%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Charging%20a%20news%20outlet%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%2C%20is%20a%20brazen%20attempt%20to%20silence%20and%20harass%20independent%20media%2C%20activists%20and%20citizens.%20We%20call%20for%20the%20immediate%20release%20of%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20Amit%20Chakravarty.%20All%20charges%20against%20NewsClick%20must%20be%20dropped%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2023%2F10%2Findia-drop-charges-and-release-newsclick-workers-and-end-harassment-of-media%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20David%20Kode%2C%20advocacy%20and%20campaigns%20lead%20at%20CIVICUS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20started%20on%20October%203%2C%20with%20the%20police%20seizing%20electronic%20devices%2C%20including%20mobile%20phones%2C%20laptops%20and%20hard%20disks%2C%20of%20journalists.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20police%20have%20questioned%20at%20least%2046%20journalists%20associated%20with%2