%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F15124209%2Folympic-games-6314253_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Saturday%2C%20October%2014%2C%20announced%20that%20India%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%E2%80%9D%20to%20host%20the%20Olympics%20in%202036%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20the%20dream%20of%20140%20crore%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1967777%5C%22%3Espeaking%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20141st%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20Session%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20important%20decisions%20regarding%20the%20future%20of%20the%20games%20are%20made.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20name%20a%20host%20city%20%E2%80%93%20but%20speculation%20suggests%20that%20Ahmedabad%20in%20Gujarat%20could%20be%20chosen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20eager%20to%20host%20the%20Olympics%20in%20the%20country.%20India%20will%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20the%20preparation%20for%20the%20successful%20organization%20of%20the%20Olympics%20in%202036%2C%20this%20is%20the%20dream%20of%20the%20140%20crore%20Indians.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20also%20wants%20to%20host%20the%20Youth%20Olympics%20in%202029%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Csports%20is%20not%20just%20for%20winning%20medals%20but%20is%20a%20medium%20to%20win%20hearts.%20Sports%20belongs%20to%20all%20for%20all.%20It%20not%20only%20prepares%20champions%20but%20also%20promotes%20peace%2C%20progress%20and%20wellness.%20Therefore%2C%20sports%20is%20another%20medium%20of%20uniting%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20never%20hosted%20the%20Olympics%20before%2C%20and%20the%20most%20high-profile%20sporting%20event%20that%20the%20country%20hosted%20was%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParis%20will%20host%20the%202024%20Olympic%20and%20Paralympic%20Games%20between%20July%20and%20August%2C%20followed%20by%20Los%20Angeles%20in%202028.%20Brisbane%20will%20host%20the%202032%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPoland%20has%20so%20far%20expressed%20interest%20in%20joining%20the%20bid%20to%20host%20the%20Olympics%20in%202036%2C%20while%20Indonesia%20and%20Mexico%20might%20also%20join%20the%20race%20to%20host%20the%202036%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20IOC%20session%20is%20expected%20to%20approve%20the%20inclusion%20of%20cricket%20and%20four%20other%20games%20as%20part%20of%20the%202028%20Los%20Angeles%20Olympics.%20Each%20host%20city%2C%20under%20IOC%20rules%20approved%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20can%20request%20the%20inclusion%20of%20several%20sports%20for%20their%20edition%20of%20the%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisers%20of%20the%20Los%20Angeles%202028%20Games%20said%20this%20week%20they%20wanted%20cricket%2C%20flag%20football%2C%20lacrosse%2C%20squash%20and%20baseball-softball%20added%20to%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20currently%20hosting%20the%20ODI%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20Indian%20team%20convincingly%20defeated%20arch-rival%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20Commenting%20on%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcommentisfree%2F2023%2Foct%2F08%2Fthe-guardian-view-on-world-cup-sportwashing-money-talks-and-what-it-says-is-troubling%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20observed%20in%20an%20editorial%20that%20if%20the%20India%20team%20is%20crowned%20one-day%20world%20cricket%20champions%20this%20year%2C%20%E2%80%9CMr%20Modi%20may%20be%20tempted%20to%20call%20an%20early%20poll%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20celebratory%20fervour%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInputs%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2F