That%20as%20you%20read%20about%20it%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20juggernaut%20at%20once%20ruthless%20and%20uncaring%20of%20individuals%20and%20their%20hopes%20or%20aspirations%20each%20time%20it%20begins%20its%20journey%20on%20some%20path%20planned%20by%20destiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECan%20we%20accept%2C%20as%20media%20persons%2C%20that%20leadership%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20is%20bringing%20forth%20vast%20changes%20in%20all%20spheres%2C%20including%20in%20your%20profession%2C%20making%20you%20feel%20small%2C%20redundant%2C%20and%20full%20of%20self-doubt%3F%20The%20laws%20proliferate%20and%20change%20so%20fast%20that%20every%20one%20of%20us%20suspects%20he%20or%20she%20may%20be%20breaking%20a%20half-understood%20new%20law%20somehow.%20And%20so%20when%20a%20citizen%20we%20know%20to%20be%20totally%20innocent%20of%20the%20charges%20levelled%20against%20him%2Fher%20is%20hauled%20and%20%E2%80%9Cheld%20back%20for%20long%20questioning%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20authorities%2C%20our%20first%20reaction%20is%20to%20wonder%20even%20if%20momentarily%20that%20maybe%20he%20has%20broken%20a%20law%20somewhere%20along%20the%20way.%20Authoritarianism%20feeds%20on%20such%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20doubt%20and%20confusion%20about%20the%20constitution.%20Hence%20the%20proliferation%20of%20decrees%20and%20ordinances%2C%20and%20bills%20being%20passed%20hurriedly%20by%20voice%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20long%20existence%20under%20such%20circumstances%20makes%20the%20people%20docile%20and%20ready%20to%20follow%20the%20new%20rules%20of%20the%20game%20unquestioningly.%20In%202023%2C%20we%20learn%20countries%20earlier%20considered%20%E2%80%98friends%E2%80%99%20must%20now%20be%20seen%20as%20unfriendly%20under%20the%20new%20treaties%20signed%20by%20those%20who%20live%20and%20work%20only%20in%20the%20vast%20time%20not%20available%20to%20us.%20The%20more%20space%20the%20Vast%20Time%20buys%20for%20the%20state%2C%20the%20less%20there%20is%20for%20us%20to%20ponder%20over%20the%20new%20developments.%20We%20accept%20projects%20and%20new%20buildings%20made%20with%20public%20money%20being%20gifted%20personally%20to%20us%20by%20the%20leadership.%20We%20accept%20becoming%20stooges%20to%20superpowers%20we%20see%20shaking%20hands%20and%20giving%20bear%20hugs%20to%20our%20leadership.%20The%20future%20shall%2C%20we%20learn%2C%20no%20longer%20grow%20organically%20out%20of%20our%20known%20historical%20past%20but%20a%20new%20world%20order%2C%20newer%20coalitions%20that%20mandate%20a%20new%20interpretation%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESchools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20institutions%20all%20must%20abandon%20old%20history%20and%20subscribe%20to%20new%20ones%20even%20if%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20sense.%20Our%20subjective%20time%20seems%20to%20have%20ceased%20to%20matter.%20Suddenly%20a%20war%20erupts%20far%20off%20but%20our%20media%20is%20feeding%20us%20a%20mish-mash%20of%20irrational%20images%2C%20myths%2C%20make-believe%2C%20illusory%20visuals%3A%20leaders%20launching%20billion%20rupee%20projects%2C%20new%20trains%2C%20new%20colleges%2C%20speaking%20to%20students%20of%20a%20new%20AI-armed%20tech-savvy%20India%2C%20flying%20off%20suddenly%20and%20seen%20next%20in%20the%20remotest%20idyllic%20setting%20praying%20to%20ancient%20gods%20with%20Vedic%20rituals.%20Kishore%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20lines%20spoken%20to%20a%20dictatorial%20mother%20come%20to%20mind%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAapne%20iss%20ghar%20ko%20Swarga%20aur%20hum%20subko%20Swargvaasee%20bnaa%20diya%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(You%20have%20made%20this%20home%20into%20heaven%20and%20we%20are%20now%20all%20heaven%20dwellers)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20irrational%2C%20you%20find%20endures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20pattern%20followed%20is%20the%20same%20all%20the%20world%20over.%20First%2C%20they%20come%20for%20those%20who%20create%20values%20to%20destroy%20those%20who%20know%20what%20those%20values%20are.%20Then%20you%20co-opt%20value%20givers%E2%80%99%20phrases%20from%20the%20abandoned%20past%20and%20use%20them%20to%20great%20effect%20in%20international%20gatherings%20of%20like-minded%20new%20friends.%20Then%20you%20hand%20the%20baton%20to%20the%20media%20and%20they%20fill%20the%20space%20with%20loud%20music%20from%20a%20totally%20make-believe%20band.%20By%20now%20one%20can%20recognise%20the%20bespoke%20spokespersons%20of%20this%20brave%20new%20world%3A%20the%20ever-furious%20moustachioed%20generals%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdomain%20experts%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20constantly%20interjecting%20anchors%20with%20their%20mile-long%20questions%20answered%20with%20more%20questions%20by%20shrieking%20spokespersons%2C%20the%20matronly%20motormouths%20with%20their%20perfectly%20lacquered%20nails%20and%20pouting%20red%20O%20mouths.%20The%20only%20unforgivable%20crime%20is%20an%20open%20confrontation%20with%20the%20real%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20media%E2%80%99s%20salvation%20is%20trying%20to%20achieve%20what%20it%20can%20no%20longer%20achieve%2C%20the%20trust%20of%20consumers.%20Most%20of%20us%20the%20world%20over%2C%20frankly%20read%20the%20papers%20and%20watch%20the%20news%20like%20%3Cstrong%3Es%3C%2Fstrong%3Etale%20jokes%20written%20by%20some%20bad%20stand-up%20comedian%20and%20send%20links%20to%20WhatsApp%20groups%20with%20three%20idiots%20laughing%20till%20tears%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F08162927%2FScreenshot-2022-06-08-at-4.29.23-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22871%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F08162927%2FScreenshot-2022-06-08-at-4.29.23-PM.png%20871w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F08162927%2FScreenshot-2022-06-08-at-4.29.23-PM-300x141.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-600527%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22410%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EArmed%20conflict%2C%20idiocy%2C%20and%20a%20disorienting%20fear%20of%20extinction%2C%20there%20is%20no%20worse%20combination.%20It%20is%20fast%20creating%20a%20monochromatic%20world%20around%20us%20all%20full%20of%20people%20with%20hollow%20eyes%2C%20zero%20attention%20span%2C%20and%20a%20great%20reluctance%20to%20dive%20deep%20into%20facts%20and%20get%20the%20context%20right%20for%20heaven%E2%80%99s%20sake.%20The%20ease%20with%20which%20the%20media%20can%20now%20manipulate%20minds%20the%20world%20over%20arises%20from%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20new%20media%20consumers.%20They%20are%20perennially%20connected%20to%20multiple%20devices%20in%20planes%2C%20in%20cafes%2C%20in%20parks%2C%20and%20even%20at%20the%20dining%20table.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20seek.%20They%20are%20content%20to%20receive.%20They%20feel%20perhaps%20withdrawing%20from%20areas%20of%20public%20involvement%20they%20will%20at%20least%20increase%20the%20private%20time%20they%20have%20and%20enjoy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20news%20of%20a%20dam%20breaking%20and%20inundating%20vast%20swathes%20of%20land%20and%20killing%20hundreds%2C%20of%20earthquakes%2C%20tsunamis%2C%20and%20cyclones%20killing%20and%20destroying%20thousands%20of%20homes%20just%20brings%20on%20no%20protest%20marches%20or%20public%20effort%20to%20bail%20out%20the%20affected.%20Those%20in%20proximity%20keep%20making%20videos%20of%20mountains%20crumbling%2C%20homes%20disappearing%20in%20gorges%2C%20and%20bombs%20reducing%20whole%20human%20clusters%20to%20ash%20and%20dust.%20Among%20those%20who%20are%20watching%20it%20on%20their%20laptops%20or%20smartphones%2C%20it%20only%20brings%20a%20sad%20shrug%20and%20rolling%20of%20eyes%2C%20%E2%80%9CAh%2C%20the%20Climate%20Change!%E2%80%99%20The%20war%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20or%20Armenia%20or%20Ukraine%20is%20similarly%20dismissed%20as%20a%20natural%20mutation%20of%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20cycles%20of%20ethnic%20warfare%E2%80%9D.%20And%20the%20media%20pushes%20its%20agenda%20further%20by%20colouring%20it%20with%20religious%20tones%20so%20strong%20that%20human%20misery%20gets%20hidden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20wonder%20loneliness%2C%20depression%20and%20drug%20addiction%20are%20on%20an%20unprecedented%20rise%20everywhere.%20You%20feel%20you%20cannot%20stop%20this%20juggernaut%2C%20you%20just%20throw%20yourself%20under%20its%20wheels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20would%20it%20mean%20if%20one%20saw%20war%20as%20it%20really%20is%3F%20It%20means%20to%20see%20human%20nature%20in%20its%20greatest%20pitch%20of%20tension%2C%20terror%2C%20and%20cruelty.%20But%20if%20the%20media%20will%2C%20as%20it%20does%20each%20day%2C%20reduce%20the%20whole%20tragedy%20to%20black%20and%20white%2C%20the%20Good%20on%20the%20one%20side%20and%20the%20Baddies%20on%20the%20other%2C%20war%20seems%20like%20a%20video%20game%20played%20indoors%20with%20little%20breaks%20for%20food%20and%20a%20quick%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20time%20our%20media%20cut%20across%20the%20linguistic%20walls%20of%20China%20to%20accept%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20great%20divide%20within%20it.%20Also%20how%20war%20magnifies%20everything%20associated%20with%20everything%20from%20history%20to%20language%3A%20emotion%2C%20fury%2C%20wild%20exultation%2C%20stubbornness%2C%20and%20xenophobia.%20They%20give%20you%20a%20high%20before%20they%20destroy%20professions%20and%20professionals.%20Real-time%20wars%20on%20the%20ground%20or%20during%20elections%20are%20waged%20mostly%20through%20information%20dissemination%20in%20local%20language%20media.%20It%20is%20one-sided%20mostly%20and%20will%20answer%20no%20nuanced%20questions%2C%20only%20old%20answers%20neatly%20copied%20and%20cut-pasted%20from%20religious%20texts%20and%20military%20leaders%E2%80%99%20biographies%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20our%20media%20today%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20tools%20for%20accurate%20information%20and%20verification%20from%20so%20many%20sources%20and%20in%20so%20many%20languages.%20It%20must%20re-establish%20the%20fast-evaporating%20relationship%20between%20ideas%20and%20structures%20among%20the%20common%20men%20and%20women.%20The%20struggle%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20earth%20is%20taking%20place%20more%20and%20more%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20language%20where%20propaganda%20wars%20are%20waged%20using%20vernaculars%20as%20an%20effective%20tool%20of%20action.%20Without%20realising%2C%20most%20war%20reporters%20seem%20to%20see%20things%20on%20the%20war%20front%20as%20the%20authorities%20wish%20them%20to%20see.%20To%20be%20independent%20as%20a%20war%20reporter%20is%20not%20necessarily%20to%20criticise%20them%20but%20to%20step%20out%20of%20false%20theories%20of%20historic%20rights%20and%20wrongs%20and%20begin%20to%20see%20and%20report%20human%20beings%20as%20fellow%20human%20beings%20rooted%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20personal%20space%20and%20personal%20reflections%2C%20capable%20of%20%E2%80%98feeling%E2%80%99%20the%20pain%20they%20describe.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697353501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19135234%2FNews-studio.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fsaakhi-media-reduces-war-video-game-news-stale-jokes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ease%20with%20which%20the%20media%20can%20now%20manipulate%20minds%20arises%20from%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20new%20media%20consumers.%20They%20are%20perennially%20connected%20to%20multiple%20devices%20in%20planes%2C%20in%20cafes%2C%20in%20parks%2C%20and%20even%20at%20the%20dining%20table.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20seek%2C%20they%20are%20content%20to%20receive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fsaakhi-media-reduces-war-video-game-news-stale-jokes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20actress%20Pip