in%20football.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Bundesliga%20and%20FC%20Schalke%2004%20for%20a%20comment%20on%20the%20matter.%20The%20copy%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20there%20is%20a%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Celtic%20Controversy%3A%20A%20Player%20Caught%20in%20the%20Storm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20conflict%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20Scotland%E2%80%99s%20Celtic%20Football%20Club%2C%20where%20Israeli%20player%20Liel%20Abada%20became%20embroiled%20in%20tensions.%20Abada%E2%80%99s%20association%20with%20Israel%20led%20to%20turmoil%20among%20the%20club%E2%80%99s%20fans%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20openly%20supported%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%2C%20Hamas.%20A%20Celtic%20support%20group%2C%20the%20Green%20Brigade%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNCCeltic%2Fstatus%2F1711735306574029008%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20expressed%20solidarity%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20Palestine%2C%20prompting%20the%20club%E2%80%99s%20board%20to%20distance%20itself.%20Abada%20faced%20intense%20pressure%20from%20his%20home%20country%20to%20sever%20ties%20with%20the%20club%2C%20a%20sentiment%20echoed%20publicly%20by%20his%20teammate%2C%20Israel%20international%20Dolev%20Haziza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.glasgowtimes.co.uk%2Fsport%2F23844790.liel-abada-meets-celtic-board-fans-palestine-display%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECeltic%E2%80%99s%20management%20supported%20Abada%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20abuse%20he%20endured%20on%20social%20media%20due%20to%20his%20association%20with%20the%20club%20amid%20the%20Gaza%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20incident%20once%20again%20illuminated%20the%20complexities%20of%20navigating%20sports%20when%20political%20conflicts%20infiltrate%20players%E2%80%99%20lives%2C%20l