ch%20I%20carry%20to%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20narrates%20Kanak.%20Around%2012%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20her%20husband%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331610%2Fsma-medication-monisha-hatkar-food-business-startup-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esole%20breadwinner%20of%20the%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20passed%20away%2C%20he%20left%20behind%20a%20shattered%20wife%20and%20son.%20Money%20was%20hard%20to%20come%20by%20and%20Kanak%20wondered%20how%20she%20would%20put%20her%20son%20through%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20today%2C%20she%20prides%20herself%20on%20creating%20a%20new%20life%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%20Ask%20her%20where%20she%20bustles%20off%20every%20morning%20with%20a%20spring%20in%20her%20step%2C%20and%20she%20says%20it%20is%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20of%20her%20happy%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKanak%20is%20referring%20to%20her%20job%20at%20the%20production%20unit%20of%20%E2%80%98Maa%20Kali%20Rabri%20Bhandar%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20many%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%20units%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Ainya.%20This%20along%20with%20another%20village%20Gangpur%20%E2%80%94%20both%20collectively%20known%20as%20Rabrigram%20for%20their%20synonymity%20with%20the%20sweet%20%E2%80%94%20are%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20prime%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%20distribution%20villages%2C%20which%20have%20given%20hundreds%20of%20women%20like%20Kanak%20both%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331511%2Fstory-behind-kuremal-mohanlal-kulfi-iconic-brand-old-delhi-haryana-farmer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20won%E2%80%99t%20deny%2C%20however%2C%20that%20work%20is%20tough%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhandar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20involves%20hours%20of%20laborious%20stirring%20of%20the%20milk%20rendering%20a%20thick%20pudding-like%